data.description: Lucky you!  This beautiful home is Priced to Sell! To say that this home has good setting would just not do it justice! This Gorgeous, updated like a New Construction, Colonial Single House has a Premium, Park like, back yard with above ground pool! Fabulous, spacious modern floor plan with very generous room sizes! Nearly new kitchen with White Cabinets, Granite countertops, Stainless steel appliances and sliding doors leading to huge Back Yard with a lovely view and privacy at same time! The First floor BONUS room with OWN full bathroom can be used for additional bedroom/in-law suite/office/playroom. The Primary Bedroom Suite is huge! Boasts a large walk-in closet and stunning Modern bathroom! All other bedrooms are generous in size as well. A full basement with high ceilings and egress window can easily become additional bedrooms, a game/media room. 2 Car Garage and long driveway allow for parking for many guests. Don't look any further, you have found it! This house is gorgeous and the seller is motivated.  Just unpack and enjoy your new life in the private piece of your own land! You get all of this in historic Morrisville! Be sure to take the 360 VIRTUAL TOUR! This home is minutes from Route 1, I-95, PA or NJ Turnpikes, NJT and Amtrak lines, Oxford Valley area, New Hope.  THIS IS A SHORT SALE SUBJECT TO BANK APPROVAL.  Information provided, including square footage numbers in listing, are from property records are deemed Reliable but NOT guaranteed; and should be verified by prospective buyers.  Bright MLS# PABU2056210
